review_blob: Love this. Curacao orange peel, cloves, cardamon and loads of spicy undertones. Quite flat, which I found a little disconcerting at first (out of bottle), but I shouldnt have worried. I now want another!
Love this. Dark, smokey, spicy. Bit strong for a session, but that aint going to stop me tonight with my 9pt cask from the brewery shop!
